1. *Hiljada* ljudi se okupilo na trgu. (A thousand people gathered in the square.)
2. *Hiljadu* puta sam ponovio taj zadatak. (I repeated that task a thousand times.)
3. Njegov dnevni prihod iznosi *hiljadu* evra. (His daily income is a thousand euros.)
4. *Hiljadama* ljudi smo se povezali preko društvenih mreža. (We connected with thousands of people through social networks.)
5. On je potrošio *hiljade* dolara na putovanje. (He spent thousands of dollars on the trip.)